"v.使…瘦弱；消瘦 【英】 v. 使瘦弱(become very thin) 【考】 反义词：fatten(养肥 ) 【记】 e+maci(瘦)+ate →瘦出去, 使…瘦弱 v. (由于饥饿)使极瘦 【根】maci瘦 【记】e出, ma妈妈: 妈妈出门六个月, 我就瘦了六十斤! 【类】apoplectic: angry = emaciated: thin狂怒的是十分发怒 = 极其瘦的是十分瘦的firmness: obstinacy = supple: spineless = thin: emaciated十分坚定是顽固 = 十分顺从的是没有勇气的 = 十分瘦的是极其瘦的 【反】fatten(v 使肥); invigorate(v 鼓舞) 【记】macerate 使消瘦；e电子 + machine 我象电子机器一样机械，背单词背得瘦弱 【相关】meager 瘦弱 emaciate (v.)  1620s (implied in emaciating), from Latin emaciatus, past participle of emaciare ""make lean, waste away,"" from ex- ""out"" (see ex-) + macies ""leanness,"" from macer ""thin"" (see macro-). Related: Emaciated; emaciating."
